      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no scratches, dings, or imperfections anywhere on the body. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by the dealership. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the heated seats, functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in like-new condition.",
